heading: Sealed Archives Dungeon Guide
content: Sealed Archives features an excellent Codex of Power aspect for survivability for Druids, the . The objectives here are fast, but the layout can be a bit confusing your first clear. It's excellent overall, and you can speed through it quickly. While every dungeon has a somewhat randomized layout, there are patterns to where objectives and bosses are located. This map will help you identify those layouts so you can complete dungeons faster and maximize your XP and loot per hour! Reviewed by
